  "title": "Beautician",
  "description": "<p><u>JOBSCOPE</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct professional waxing and body treatments</li>\n  <li>recommend suitable waxing and skin therapy programme, products and packages to the customers.</li>\n  <li>Sales of packages and products to the customers.</li>\n  <li>Follow up treatment results with the customers.</li>\n  <li>Ensure booking appointments are recorded in the POS system accordingly.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u>REQUIREMENT</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Full-Time/Permanent Part-Time Positions.</li>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least a Primary/Sec Sch/\"N\" or \"O\" Level, Professional Certificate such as CIDESCO / CIBTAC / ITEC / NITEC in Beauty and Wellness or relevant certifications.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of working as Beautician / Facial and Body therapist in an established Spa/Aesthetic Clinic.</li>\n  <li>Well-groomed and pleasant personality.</li>\n  <li>Willing to work on weekends and Public Holidays.</li>\n</ul>",
